{"id":232322909,"title":"#分享 #演講 「作者説了算？當代視覺藝術的詮釋爭論」","content":"http://i.imgur.com/zaO6wIJ.jpg\n\n第一次讀到林斯諺的文字，是他在沃草烙哲學的哲普文章〈解讀藝術作品，為何需要考慮作者意圖？〉。當時十分訝異於他「與大眾對話」的能力，畢竟藝術哲學並不像應用倫理學或政治哲學一樣和日常生活、社會議題相關，要能把這樣的哲學理論說得引人入勝十分不容易。後來讀了他的小說，在《無名之女》和《馬雅任務》的字裡行間，可以感受到他對這些知識的強烈激情。\n\n明天斯諺老師有一場關於視覺藝術的演講，討論「當代視覺藝術的詮釋爭議」。大家可以參考看看。老師的聲音真的很好聽，聽他演講和講課真的是感官和智性的享受！ \n\n活動資訊：\nhttps://www.facebook.com/events/521753895282418/ \n林斯諺臉書： \nhttps://www.facebook.com/ellerysyl/","excerpt":"第一次讀到林斯諺的文字，是他在沃草烙哲學的哲普文章〈解讀藝術作品，為何需要考慮作者意圖？〉。當時十分訝異於他「與大眾對話」的能力，畢竟藝術哲學並不像應用倫理學或政治哲學一樣和日常生活、社會議題相關，要","anonymousSchool":false,"anonymousDepartment":true,"pinned":false,"forumId":"2bb20844-07ec-41d3-830f-ae551fc31246","replyId":null,"createdAt":"2019-10-18T06:32:47.118Z","updatedAt":"2019-10-18T06:32:47.118Z","commentCount":0,"likeCount":1,"tags":[],"topics":["演講","林斯諺"],"supportedReactions":null,"withNickname":false,"reportReason":"","hiddenByAuthor":false,"meta":{"layout":"classic"},"forumName":"課程","forumAlias":"course","school":"輔仁大學","replyTitle":null,"gender":"F","personaSubscriptable":true,"reactions":[{"id":"286f599c-f86a-4932-82f0-f5a06f1eca03","count":1}],"hidden":false,"customStyle":null,"isSuspiciousAccount":false,"layout":"classic","withImages":true,"withVideos":false,"media":[{"url":"http://i.imgur.com/zaO6wIJ.jpg"}],"reportReasonText":"","mediaMeta":[{"id":"02401aaf-76a3-4010-b4a1-b1e3a13ffda3","url":"https://i.imgur.com/zaO6wIJl.jpg","normalizedUrl":"https://i.imgur.com/zaO6wIJl.jpg","thumbnail":"https://i.imgur.com/zaO6wIJl.jpg","type":"image/thumbnail","tags":["ANNOTATED"],"createdAt":"2019-10-18T06:32:47.118Z","updatedAt":"2019-10-18T06:32:47.118Z"},{"id":"02401aaf-76a3-4010-b4a1-b1e3a13ffda3","url":"http://i.imgur.com/zaO6wIJ.jpg","normalizedUrl":"https://imgur.com/zaO6wIJ","thumbnail":"https://i.imgur.com/zaO6wIJl.jpg","type":"image/imgur","tags":["ANNOTATED"],"createdAt":"2019-10-18T06:32:47.118Z","updatedAt":"2019-10-18T06:32:47.118Z"}],"postAvatar":""}